==English==

===Noun phrase===
'''[[hyperbolic]] [[cosine]]'''

#{{mathematics}} a [[hyperbolic function]] that is written in symbol [[cosh]] and defined as the following:
:<math>\cosh(x) = \frac{e^x + e^{-x}}{2}</math>

